seo: CVE-2018-12613,Phpmyadmin,远程文件包含漏洞,漏洞检测,指纹识别
summary: 该插件用于检测 Phpmyadmin 中的 CVE-2018-12613 远程文件包含漏洞，同时进行指纹识别以确认目标系统是否为 Phpmyadmin。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the CVE-2018-12613 Remote File Inclusion vulnerability in Phpmyadmin and perform fingerprint identification to confirm whether the target system is Phpmyadmin.
